ExportV5.Title: Export V5
ExportV5.ShortHelp: Exports the selected objects as CATIA V5 files.
ExportV5.LongHelp:
Select one or more objects and click the command. In the Export V5 dialog box, enter the target directory for the CATIA V5 files and the export report.

If you do not want to overwrite CATIA V5 files that already exist in the target directory with a same filename , select the Keep a copy of the existing file in case of conflict in the disk option.
